Module DescribeProcess¶

This module parses OGC Web Processing Service (WPS) DescribeProcess request.

Class Post¶

class pywps.Parser.DescribeProcess.Post(wps)¶

Parses input request obtained via HTTP POST encoding - should be XML file.

Class Get¶

class pywps.Parser.DescribeProcess.Get(wps)¶

Parses input request obtained via HTTP GET encoding.
